1. download node.js and mongodb(and add them to your path)
2. in cmd, go to project directory.
3. (I've installed npm (npm init), nodemon (npm install --save-dev nodemon),
 express (npm install express --save), mongoose (npm install mongoose --save),
 cors (npm install cors)
4. commands "mongod" and "npm run start" in proj dir to start the server
5. localhost port: 3000